clone and run npm i 
to start app => npm run dev

install typescript =>  sudo npm i -g typescript 

generate tsconfig.json => tsc --init

generate package.json => npm init -y

install express => npm i express

install dev dependencies => npm i -D typescript ts-node nodemon @types/node @types/express

add scripts in package.json => "scripts": {
    "start":"node dist/app.js",
    "dev":"nodemon src/app.ts",
    "build":"tsc -p ." // generates ts compiled into dist folder
  },
